snippet.title: Omega Labyrinth Z - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The quest for the breasts begins! 

PQube is excited to announce that the most outrageous dungeon crawling RPG of them all, Omega Labyrinth Z, is coming to Europe and North America for PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita in Spring 2018!

Come chat to us on our PQube Discord server! 
https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU
